{"word":"φλεγέθω","slug":"φλεγέθω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>φλεγέθω</b></el> <el>(φλεγέθω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>poetic form of <a href='S:φλέγω'><el>φλέγω</el></a>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:transitive'>trans.</a> <i>to burn, scorch, burn up</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>ὄφρα πυρὶ φλεγεθοίατο νεκροί</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <i>to blaze, flare up</i>, of fire, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; of the sun, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}